# Never commit plaintext proposal source. Plaintext lives in the skella-proposals
# skill workspace at ~/workspace/skills/user/skella-proposals/proposals/<slug>.json.
# Only the encrypted ciphertext + salt + iv (in proposals/<slug>/index.html) is safe.
proposals/*.json
proposals/**/*.json

